  (b) MODIFICATION: Modify the Software for internal use only.

  (c) SELF-HOSTING: Deploy the Software on infrastructure controlled by the
      Licensee to serve the Licensee's own end-users.

Note: Use of the Hosted API at https://safe.teosegypt.com does not require
a License Key and is governed by the Terms of Service at
https://safe.teosegypt.com/legal.html

